01:56:36.620 --> 01:56:40.680
But I knew that he told me he just returned from Camp David.

01:56:40.820 --> 01:56:42.080
And it was at Christmas when he gave it to me.

01:56:42.080 --> 01:56:43.360
Oh, so he totally told you that.

01:56:43.360 --> 01:56:43.620
Yeah.

01:56:44.200 --> 01:56:44.560
Yeah.

01:56:44.780 --> 01:56:45.080
Wow.

01:56:45.660 --> 01:56:50.760
And he said, I was at the dinner table with the president and handed me that napkin.

01:56:50.760 --> 01:56:51.120
He said that.

01:56:51.280 --> 01:56:51.480
Yeah.

01:56:51.560 --> 01:56:52.680
Okay, so he did tell you that.

01:56:52.800 --> 01:56:53.460
He didn't tell me.

01:56:53.520 --> 01:56:55.940
He briefed him, but he did give me the napkin and this.

01:56:55.940 --> 01:56:56.260
Whoa.

01:56:56.400 --> 01:56:57.040
And this.

01:56:57.400 --> 01:56:57.620
Yeah.

01:56:58.320 --> 01:56:59.100
And you believe him.

01:56:59.500 --> 01:56:59.760
Yeah.

01:57:00.040 --> 01:57:01.200
Had no reason not to.

01:57:01.900 --> 01:57:03.800
Have you ever caught him in a lie?

01:57:04.340 --> 01:57:04.640
No.

01:57:05.040 --> 01:57:05.320
Ever?

01:57:06.240 --> 01:57:07.000
I wouldn't.

01:57:07.320 --> 01:57:08.560
No, not that I can recall.

01:57:08.560 --> 01:57:12.720
Everything he said has either come out to be true or you're waiting for confirmation.

01:57:12.840 --> 01:57:13.080
Right.

01:57:13.440 --> 01:57:13.580
Right.

01:57:14.040 --> 01:57:14.400
Wow.

01:57:15.140 --> 01:57:17.380
Have you independently verified some of the things that he said?

01:57:17.380 --> 01:57:19.720
Some of what he's told me, yeah, 100%.

01:57:19.720 --> 01:57:21.020
Is there an example of that?

01:57:22.680 --> 01:57:28.820
No, but it's just, you know, it'd be like, it's just so hard to pinpoint any one thing.

01:57:28.900 --> 01:57:29.160
Sure.

01:57:29.620 --> 01:57:33.740
Or like, I don't know, some of the things about how the NRO or NASA work together.

01:57:34.020 --> 01:57:35.540
Have you been able to verify anything?

01:57:35.540 --> 01:57:36.340
Yeah, absolutely.

01:57:36.620 --> 01:57:36.840
Yeah.

01:57:37.100 --> 01:57:37.380
Yeah.

01:57:37.380 --> 01:57:46.000
Do you think that the Big Dipper or URSA major has anything to do with the UFO phenomena?

