I can take you out at night and face one certain direction and only have a hole to look through

01:58:08.500 --> 01:58:10.840
that direction and it'll come from there.

01:58:10.840 --> 01:58:15.440
We can turn in any direction and focus there and that's where it'll come from.

01:58:16.440 --> 01:58:22.840
So do you think the Vatican and the president and whoever, Tim Taylor, you know, the hammer,

01:58:23.080 --> 01:58:25.140
do you think they're all coordinating in some way?

01:58:25.280 --> 01:58:29.820
Like this archangel, the Vatican and the president, or what do you think the connection is there?

01:58:29.820 --> 01:58:31.260
I don't have a clue.

01:58:33.040 --> 01:58:35.100
I'm just telling you what I was told, right?

01:58:35.260 --> 01:58:35.600
Yeah.

01:58:35.600 --> 01:58:42.200
So I've been told a lot of things, but he told me about the movie, the Adjustment Bureau

01:58:42.200 --> 01:58:44.020
and the story about the hammer.

01:58:44.260 --> 01:58:44.500
Yeah.

